															</div>
				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/decibelles" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2005044); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2005044&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610252581" alt="Decibelles" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2005044)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/decibelles" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2005044); return false;" >Decibelles</a></span> <span class="odate time_1512455806 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">05 Dec 2017 06:36</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-3646062">
									

<p>I'll be making edits to this tale over the next few days to further the format screw, as well as upload more avatars. Once I do so, this text will be deleted.</p>
<hr />
<p>Credits:</p>
<p>Decibelles' avatar is done by <a href="https://smileknife.tumblr.com/post/167168943848/scp-3090-lesbian-gamergirl-with-a-tv-for-a-head">smileknife</a>, used with permission.</p>
<p>Bohemian Rhapsody's avatar is done by <a href="https://vvolny.deviantart.com/art/light-Bulb-107526926">vvolny</a>, and I will be fulfilling the further requirements to use/edit that photo in the next day.</p>
<p>Perfect Day's avatar is my own creation.</p>
<p>Snow Halation's avatar is done by <a href="https://zhange-art.tumblr.com/">Zhange</a> (on the site as <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zhange" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2938475); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2938475&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1512466699" alt="Zhange" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2938475)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zhange" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2938475); return false;">Zhange</a></span>, used with permission. In the interest of transparency, it is fanart of the show <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Land_of_the_Lustrous">Land of the Lustrous</a>.</p>
<p><a href="http://ja.scp-wiki.net/835love">闇子様教を広めるスレッド</a>, written by EFU and coding by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/c-take" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2872372); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2872372&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1512466699" alt="C-take" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2872372)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/c-take" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2872372); return false;">C-take</a></span>, with modifications by me as I needed them, forms the basis of the final offset. If anyone knows how to fix the issues with the mock-karma/avatar stuff not displaying properly, PLEASE let me know. I spent four hours on that before I gave up. The three big critiques were used with express permission from three different authors whom I will not name just in case (unless they want to name themselves in this thread?).</p>
<p>Thank you to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/taffeta" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2221240); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2221240&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1512466699" alt="Taffeta" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2221240)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/taffeta" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2221240); return false;">Taffeta</a></span> whom, without them, this tale series literally could not exist. Their technical expertise is literally and absolutely what makes this shit tick. Special thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rejekyll" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1225984); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1225984&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1512466699" alt="Rejekyll" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1225984)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rejekyll" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1225984); return false;">Rejekyll</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/randomini" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1379080); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1379080&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1512466699" alt="Randomini" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1379080)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/randomini" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1379080); return false;">Randomini</a></span> for technical help as well (some of this code was taken from <a href="/scp-2342">SCP-2342</a>). Sorry for posting this in the early hours of Tuesday instead of Monday. This took me longer to code than to write (and it took me ten hours to write), and has caused me to have a meltdown. Life reflects art, as art reflects life, etc..</p>
<p>I'm gonna fucking sleep.</p>
<hr />
<p>Updates Mondays and Thursdays.</p>

